snippet: Keegan Bradley shot a one-under-par 69, good enough for a three-stroke lead after two rounds in the Byron Nelson Championship in Irving, Tex.
abstract: Keegan Bradley takes second-round lead at Byron Nelson Championship; other golf news noted.
